OL,3,CHas Keir Starmer proved he didn't lie
OL,4,Cto MPs?
OL,6,FDowning Street has published a letter
OL,7,Fby the previous cabinet secretary,
OL,8,FChris Wormald, on whether due process
OL,9,Fwas followed - as claimed by the prime
OL,10,Fminister - in the appointment (and
OL,11,Fsacking) of Peter Mandelson.
OL,13,FAs of September 16 last year, Wormald
OL,14,Fwrote to Sir Keir Starmer that
OL,15,F"appropriate processes were followed".
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
