OL,3,CHas Keir Starmer proved he didn't lie
OL,4,Cto MPs?
OL,6,FIt says that when Mandelson was
OL,7,Fgranted deep vetting status, "the FCDO
OL,8,Falso immediately took on the task of
OL,9,Fworking with Lord Mandelson to
OL,10,Funderstand and mitigate conflicts of
OL,11,Finterest in advance of his departure
OL,12,Ffor Washington".
OL,14,FThis implies that issues were raised
OL,15,Fin the vetting process.
OL,17,FSo why didn't Starmer seemingly ever
OL,18,Fask about these?
OL,26,@oD@^OUtD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
