OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777334614
OL,3,CHas Keir Starmer proved he didn't lie
OL,4,Cto MPs?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIf he had, surely he would have
OL,12,Flearned that the Foreign Office gave
OL,13,Fvetting approval after mitigating UK
OL,14,FSecurity Vetting's concerns, which we
OL,15,Fnow know were marked as a red flag.
OL,17,FStarmer would therefore not have felt
OL,18,Fthe need to sack Olly Robbins as
OL,19,Fpermanent under secretary at the
OL,20,FForeign Office for never telling him
OL,21,FUKSV's verdict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
