OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777334614
OL,3,CHas Keir Starmer proved he didn't lie
OL,4,Cto MPs?
OL,6,FAnd by the way, the letter also
OL,7,Fcontains this statement of the
OL,8,Fobvious, but which is the only fact
OL,9,Fthat really matters about the
OL,10,FMandelson appointment: "This was a
OL,11,Fdirect prime ministerial appointment
OL,12,Ffrom outside both the Diplomatic and
OL,13,FHome Civil Service."
OL,15,FIn other words, the PM really has no
OL,16,Fone to blame but himself for the
OL,17,FMandelson appointment, though plenty
OL,18,Fof others have lost their jobs.
OL,26,@rD@XOUuD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
