PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777334614
OL,3,CHas Keir Starmer proved he didn't lie
OL,4,Cto MPs?
OL,6,FPS, government sources say that
OL,7,FWormald's reference to the Foreign
OL,8,FOffice putting in place mitigations
OL,9,Ffor Mandelson's "conflicts of
OL,10,Finterest" does not refer to what the
OL,11,Fvetting of Mandelson threw up, and are
OL,12,Fnot the mitigations Robbins mentioned
OL,13,Fin his evidence to MPs.
OL,15,FThey are more routine than that, they
OL,16,Finsist - the "normal" management of
OL,17,Foutside business interests on behalf
OL,18,Fof someone going into government - and
OL,19,Fwould not have triggered the PM to
OL,20,Fsmell something more troubling.
OL,26,@qD@QOUrD@IO]xD@NOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
